      "description": "This vehicle is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep, mirror-like finish and zero imperfections, while the interior remains in 'as-new' state with no signs of wear or use. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been garage-kept and maintained to the highest standards. Buyers can expect a car that looks and drives exactly as it did when it first left the dealership floor.",
