      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a well-maintained example of a reliable daily driver. The exterior paint retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the leather upholstery is supple, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronic features, including the dual-zone climate control and infotainment system, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in robust health with a documented service history. The engine idles smoothly, the transmission provides crisp shifts, and the brakes feel firm. It recently received an oil service and a fresh set of premium tires with plenty of tread remaining. This is a dependable, honest car that drives as well as it looks.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
